trans-unit.source: Contains conversion routines used by XSLT.
trans-unit.target: 包含 XSLT 使用的轉換常式。

trans-unit.source: These conversions fall into the following three categories: - Internal type to internal type: These are conversions from one of the five XSLT types to another of the five types.
trans-unit.target: 這些轉換可分為下列三個類別:-內部類型的內部型別︰ 這些是五個 XSLT 型別之間的轉換五種類型。

trans-unit.source: - External type to internal type: These are conversions from any of the Xsd types to one of the five XSLT types.
trans-unit.target: 的內部類型外部型別︰ 這些是從任何 Xsd 型別轉換為其中五個 XSLT 型別。

trans-unit.source: - Internal type to external type: These are conversions from one of the five XSLT types to any of the Xsd types.
trans-unit.target: 外部類型的內部型別︰ 這些是從其中五個 XSLT 型別轉換為任何 Xsd 型別。

trans-unit.source: Ensures that the specified sequence of objects is not a result tree fragment and that it can be converted to a node set.
trans-unit.target: 可確保將指定之物件序列不是結果樹狀片段，而且它可以轉換為節點集。
